high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall on the other side of the room then turn left walk until you're between the chairs by the table then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the black plate you see on the table in front of you.

Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the white chair then turn right and take a step then turn left and take a step then turn right and walk to the small coffee table then turn right to face it.
Put the plate near the tables bottom right corner.

Turn right and walk almost to the white chair then turn left and walk to the table then turn left and walk until you've cleared the table then turn right and walk almost to the end of the table then turn right.
Pick up the black plate you see on the table.
Walk back to where you put the first plate.
Put this plate to the right of the first.
anns.task_desc: Put two black plates on the table.

high_descs: Move across the room to stand on the other side of the kitchen table, which puts you between the table and wall.
Pick up the black plate from the table.
Carry the plate across the room and into the living room until you get to the coffee table.
Place the plate on the coffee table opposite the open box.
Move back through the living room and kitchen to the other end of the table where you see another plate.
Pick the plate up from the table.
Carry the plate back through the kitchen and living room to the coffee table again.
Place the plate on the coffee table to the right of the other plate you  previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two plates to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around walk across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the middle of the far side of the wooden table.
Pick up the grey plate that is closest to the laptop on the wooden table.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk across the room to the coffee table.
Place the grey plate on the coffee table to the right of the golden statue.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the left end of the wooden table.
Pick up the grey plate off of the wooden table.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk around the couch to the coffee table.
Put the grey plate on the coffee table above the plate that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two grey plates to the coffee table.
